{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"Talking about empowerment is odd,"},{"time":3659,"text":"because when we talk about empowerment,"},{"time":5761,"text":"what affects us most are the stories."},{"time":8967,"text":"So I want to begin with an everyday story."},{"time":12179,"text":"What is it really like to be a young woman in India?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":16702,"text":"Now, I've spent the last 27 years of my life"},{"time":18974,"text":"in India, lived in three small towns,"},{"time":21073,"text":"two major cities,"},{"time":22889,"text":"and I've had several experiences."},{"time":26118,"text":"When I was seven,"},{"time":27974,"text":"a private tutor who used to come home"},{"time":29931,"text":"to teach me mathematics molested me."},{"time":34646,"text":"He would put his hand up my skirt."},{"time":40794,"text":"He put his hand up my skirt and told me"},{"time":43970,"text":"he knew how to make me feel good."},{"time":47930,"text":"At 17, a boy from my high school"},{"time":51060,"text":"circulated an email"},{"time":52507,"text":"detailing all the sexually aggressive things"},{"time":54940,"text":"he could do to me"},{"time":57704,"text":"because I didn't pay attention to him."},{"time":61789,"text":"At 19, I helped a friend"},{"time":65500,"text":"whose parents had forcefully\nmarried her to an older man"},{"time":68592,"text":"escape an abusive marriage."},{"time":72259,"text":"At 21, when my friend and I were walking"},{"time":74401,"text":"down the road one afternoon,"},{"time":78734,"text":"a man pulled down his pants"},{"time":80273,"text":"and masturbated in front of us."},{"time":83483,"text":"We called people for help, and nobody came."},{"time":87910,"text":"At 25, when I was walking home one evening,"},{"time":92900,"text":"two men on a motorcycle attacked me."},{"time":95726,"text":"I spent two nights in the hospital"},{"time":97843,"text":"recovering from trauma and injuries."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101085,"text":"So throughout my life, I've seen women —"},{"time":106305,"text":"family, friends, colleagues —"},{"time":108171,"text":"live through these experiences,"},{"time":110964,"text":"and they seldom talk about it."},{"time":114137,"text":"So in simple words, life in India is not easy."},{"time":118777,"text":"But today I'm not going to talk to you about this fear."},{"time":122295,"text":"I'm going to talk to you about an interesting path"},{"time":124049,"text":"of learning that this fear took me on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128427,"text":"So, what happened one night in December 2012"},{"time":131930,"text":"changed my life."},{"time":133704,"text":"So a young girl, a 23-year-old student,"},{"time":137000,"text":"boarded a bus in Delhi with her male friend."},{"time":141904,"text":"There were six men on the bus, young men"},{"time":144513,"text":"who you might encounter every day in India,"},{"time":147591,"text":"and the chilling account of what followed"},{"time":149923,"text":"was played over and over again"},{"time":151667,"text":"in the Indian and international media."},{"time":154491,"text":"This girl was raped repeatedly,"},{"time":157765,"text":"forcefully penetrated with a blunt rod,"},{"time":160745,"text":"beaten, bitten, and left to die."},{"time":163996,"text":"Her friend was gagged, attacked,"},{"time":166000,"text":"and knocked unconscious."},{"time":169577,"text":"She died on the 29th of December."},{"time":173761,"text":"And at a time when most of us here"},{"time":175739,"text":"were preparing to welcome the new year,"},{"time":178242,"text":"India plunged into darkness."},{"time":181479,"text":"For the first time in our history,"},{"time":184645,"text":"men and women in Indian cities"},{"time":186823,"text":"woke up to the horrific truth"},{"time":189014,"text":"about the true state of women in the country."},{"time":192536,"text":"Now, like many other young women,"},{"time":194955,"text":"I was absolutely terrified."},{"time":197149,"text":"I couldn't believe that something like this"},{"time":198416,"text":"could happen in a national capital."},{"time":201591,"text":"I was angry and I was frustrated,"},{"time":204144,"text":"but most of all, I felt utterly, completely helpless."},{"time":208247,"text":"But really, what do you do, right?"},{"time":210388,"text":"Some write blogs, some ignore it,"},{"time":212413,"text":"some join protests."},{"time":214145,"text":"I did all of it. In fact, that was what everyone was doing"},{"time":216710,"text":"two years ago."},{"time":218388,"text":"So the media was filled with stories about"},{"time":221367,"text":"all the horrific deeds"},{"time":223133,"text":"that Indian men are capable of."},{"time":225237,"text":"They were compared to animals,"},{"time":226472,"text":"sexually repressed beasts."},{"time":228659,"text":"In fact, so alien and unthinkable was this event"},{"time":232663,"text":"in an Indian mind"},{"time":233977,"text":"that the response from the Indian media,"},{"time":236393,"text":"public and politicians proved one point:"},{"time":240300,"text":"No one knew what to do."},{"time":242179,"text":"And no one wanted to be responsible for it."},{"time":244776,"text":"In fact, these were a few insensitive comments"},{"time":247260,"text":"which were made in the media"},{"time":248441,"text":"by prominent people"},{"time":250468,"text":"in response to sexual violence\nagainst women in general."},{"time":254624,"text":"So the first one is made by a member of parliament,"},{"time":257826,"text":"the second one is made by a spiritual leader,"},{"time":261219,"text":"and the third one was actually\nthe defendants' lawyer"},{"time":263930,"text":"when the girl was fighting for her life"},{"time":265776,"text":"and she passed away."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268630,"text":"Now, as a woman watching this day after day,"},{"time":272483,"text":"I was tired."},{"time":274283,"text":"So as a writer and gender activist,"},{"time":275927,"text":"I have written extensively on women,"},{"time":279176,"text":"but this time, I realized it was different,"},{"time":281822,"text":"because a part of me realized"},{"time":283403,"text":"I was a part of that young woman too,"},{"time":285751,"text":"and I decided I wanted to change this."},{"time":287929,"text":"So I did something spontaneous, hasty."},{"time":291960,"text":"I logged on to a citizen journalism platform"},{"time":294506,"text":"called iReport,"},{"time":295962,"text":"and I recorded a video talking about"},{"time":298713,"text":"what the scene was like in Bangalore."},{"time":300693,"text":"I talked about how I felt,"},{"time":302380,"text":"I talked about the ground realities,"},{"time":303722,"text":"and I talked about the frustrations of living in India."},{"time":309227,"text":"In a few hours, the blog was shared widely,"},{"time":312845,"text":"and comments and thoughts poured in"},{"time":314680,"text":"from across the world."},{"time":316340,"text":"In that moment, a few things occurred to me."},{"time":320015,"text":"One, technology was always at hand"},{"time":323743,"text":"for many young women like me."},{"time":326960,"text":"Two, like me, most young women"},{"time":330504,"text":"hardly use it to express their views."},{"time":333925,"text":"Three, I realized for the first time"},{"time":337849,"text":"that my voice mattered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":340707,"text":"So in the months that followed,"},{"time":343440,"text":"I covered a trail of events in Bangalore"},{"time":345487,"text":"which had no space in the mainstream news."},{"time":349469,"text":"In Cubbon Park, which is a big park in Bangalore,"},{"time":352240,"text":"I gathered with over 100 others"},{"time":353840,"text":"when groups of young men came forward"},{"time":355749,"text":"to wear skirts to prove that clothing"},{"time":357561,"text":"does not invite rape."},{"time":361241,"text":"When I reported about these events,"},{"time":363075,"text":"I felt I had charge, I felt like I had a channel"},{"time":366168,"text":"to release all the emotions I had inside me."},{"time":370337,"text":"I attended the town hall march"},{"time":372409,"text":"when students held up signs saying"},{"time":374343,"text":"\"Kill them, hang them.\""},{"time":376872,"text":"\"You wouldn't do this to your mothers or sisters.\""},{"time":380699,"text":"I went to a candlelight vigil"},{"time":382177,"text":"where citizens gathered together"},{"time":384280,"text":"to talk about the issue of sexual violence openly,"},{"time":388237,"text":"and I recorded a lot of blogs"},{"time":390277,"text":"in response to how worrying the situation was"},{"time":392980,"text":"in India at that point."},{"time":394249,"text":"[\"I am born with sisters and cousin who now live in cities and abroad but they never talk to me or complain about their daily difficulties like you say\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":395898,"text":"Now, the reactions confused me."},{"time":397357,"text":"While supportive comments poured\nin from across the world,"},{"time":400227,"text":"as did vicious ones."},{"time":402241,"text":"So some called me a hypocrite."},{"time":403675,"text":"Some called me a victim, a rape apologist."},{"time":406438,"text":"Some even said I had a political motive."},{"time":409403,"text":"But this one comment kind of describes"},{"time":411523,"text":"what we are discussing here today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416330,"text":"But I was soon to learn that this was not all."},{"time":419440,"text":"As empowered as I felt"},{"time":421429,"text":"with the new liberty that this"},{"time":422879,"text":"citizen journalism channel gave me,"},{"time":425236,"text":"I found myself in an unfamiliar situation."},{"time":428570,"text":"So sometime last August, I logged onto Facebook"},{"time":431737,"text":"and I was looking through my news feed,"},{"time":433140,"text":"and I noticed there was a link"},{"time":435183,"text":"that was being shared by my friends."},{"time":436856,"text":"I clicked on the link; it led me back"},{"time":439039,"text":"to a report uploaded by an American girl"},{"time":443114,"text":"called Michaela Cross."},{"time":445322,"text":"The report was titled,"},{"time":446710,"text":"\"India: The story you never wanted to hear.\""},{"time":449951,"text":"And in this report, she recounted her firsthand"},{"time":453096,"text":"account of facing sexual harassment in India."},{"time":456796,"text":"She wrote, \"There is no way to prepare for the eyes,"},{"time":460763,"text":"the eyes that every day stared"},{"time":462850,"text":"with such entitlement at my body,"},{"time":465574,"text":"with no change of expression"},{"time":467424,"text":"whether I met their gaze or not."},{"time":470072,"text":"Walking to the fruit seller's or the tailor's,"},{"time":473210,"text":"I got stares so sharp"},{"time":475309,"text":"that they sliced away bits of me piece by piece.\""},{"time":478746,"text":"She called India a traveler's\nheaven and a woman's hell."},{"time":482640,"text":"She said she was stalked, groped,"},{"time":484656,"text":"and masturbated at."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486253,"text":"Now, late that evening, the report went viral."},{"time":488692,"text":"It was on news channels across the world."},{"time":492304,"text":"Everyone was discussing it."},{"time":493910,"text":"It had over a million views,"},{"time":495018,"text":"a thousand comments and shares,"},{"time":496923,"text":"and I found myself witnessing"},{"time":498837,"text":"a very similar thing."},{"time":501401,"text":"The media was caught in this vicious cycle"},{"time":504097,"text":"of opinion and outburst"},{"time":506395,"text":"and no outcome whatsoever."},{"time":509700,"text":"So that night, as I sat wondering"},{"time":512105,"text":"how I should respond,"},{"time":513437,"text":"I found myself filled with doubt."},{"time":515847,"text":"You see, as a writer, I approached this issue"},{"time":519208,"text":"as an observer,"},{"time":521586,"text":"as an Indian, I felt embarrassment and disbelief,"},{"time":525964,"text":"and as an activist, I looked\nat it as a defender of rights,"},{"time":530443,"text":"but as a citizen journalist,"},{"time":532578,"text":"I suddenly felt very vulnerable."},{"time":535852,"text":"I mean, here she was, a young woman"},{"time":538183,"text":"who was using a channel to talk about"},{"time":539583,"text":"her experience just as I was,"},{"time":541731,"text":"and yet I felt unsettled."},{"time":544545,"text":"You see, no one ever tells you"},{"time":546467,"text":"that true empowerment comes from giving yourself"},{"time":549407,"text":"the permission to think and act."},{"time":551783,"text":"Empowerment is often made to sound as if"},{"time":554245,"text":"it's an ideal, it's a wonderful outcome."},{"time":557442,"text":"When we talk about empowerment, we often"},{"time":559274,"text":"talk about giving people access to materials,"},{"time":562559,"text":"giving them access to tools."},{"time":565295,"text":"But the thing is, empowerment is an emotion."},{"time":567744,"text":"It's a feeling."},{"time":569206,"text":"The first step to empowerment"},{"time":571938,"text":"is to give yourself the authority,"},{"time":574818,"text":"the key to independent will,"},{"time":576793,"text":"and for women everywhere,"},{"time":578393,"text":"no matter who we are or where we come from,"},{"time":580941,"text":"that is the most difficult step."},{"time":584261,"text":"We fear the sound of our own voice,"},{"time":586870,"text":"for it means admission, but it is this that gives us"},{"time":589656,"text":"the power to change our environment."},{"time":592740,"text":"Now in this situation where I was faced"},{"time":594581,"text":"with so many different kinds of realities,"},{"time":597267,"text":"I was unsure how to judge,"},{"time":598753,"text":"because I didn't know what it would mean for me."},{"time":601838,"text":"I feared to judge because I\ndidn't know what it would be"},{"time":604843,"text":"if I didn't support the same view as this girl."},{"time":608124,"text":"I didn't know what it would mean for me"},{"time":609490,"text":"if I was challenging someone else's truth."},{"time":614370,"text":"But yet, it was simple."},{"time":615863,"text":"I had to make a decision:"},{"time":617312,"text":"Should I speak up or should I stay quiet?"},{"time":620502,"text":"So after a lot of thought,"},{"time":622786,"text":"I recorded a video blog in response,"},{"time":625282,"text":"and I told Michaela, well,"},{"time":627252,"text":"there are different sides to India,"},{"time":629955,"text":"and I also tried to explain"},{"time":635364,"text":"that things would be okay"},{"time":637425,"text":"and I expressed my regret for what she had faced."},{"time":640091,"text":"And a few days later, I was invited to talk"},{"time":642692,"text":"on air with her,"},{"time":644061,"text":"and for the first time, I reached out to this girl"},{"time":648181,"text":"who I had never met, who was so far away,"},{"time":650982,"text":"but yet I felt so close to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":653820,"text":"Since this report came to light,"},{"time":656350,"text":"more young people than ever"},{"time":658655,"text":"were discussing sexual harassment on the campus,"},{"time":662006,"text":"and the university that Michaela belonged to"},{"time":664797,"text":"gave her the assistance she needed."},{"time":668645,"text":"The university even took measures"},{"time":670990,"text":"to train its students to equip them"},{"time":673049,"text":"with the skills that they need"},{"time":674685,"text":"to confront challenges such as harassment,"},{"time":678155,"text":"and for the first the time, I felt I wasn't alone."},{"time":682448,"text":"You see, if there's anything that I've learned"},{"time":684534,"text":"as an active citizen journalist"},{"time":687169,"text":"over the past few years,"},{"time":690252,"text":"it is our dire lack as a society to actively find"},{"time":694225,"text":"avenues where our voices can be heard."},{"time":697222,"text":"We don't realize that when we are standing up,"},{"time":701526,"text":"we are not just standing up as individuals,"},{"time":703368,"text":"we are standing up for our communities,"},{"time":706605,"text":"our friends, our peers."},{"time":708464,"text":"Most of us say that women are denied their rights,"},{"time":711837,"text":"but the truth is, oftentimes,"},{"time":714213,"text":"women deny themselves these rights."},{"time":717613,"text":"In a recent survey in India,"},{"time":720250,"text":"95 percent of the women who work in I.T.,"},{"time":724781,"text":"aviation, hospitality and call centers,"},{"time":728197,"text":"said they didn't feel safe returning home alone"},{"time":730764,"text":"after work in the late hours or in the evening."},{"time":734150,"text":"In Bangalore, where I come from,"},{"time":735551,"text":"this number is 85 percent."},{"time":738017,"text":"In rural areas in India,"},{"time":740563,"text":"if anything is to go by the recent"},{"time":743720,"text":"gang rapes in Badaun and acid attacks in Odisha"},{"time":746287,"text":"and Aligarh are supposed to go by,"},{"time":748308,"text":"we need to act really soon."}]},{"cues":[{"time":751885,"text":"Don't get me wrong,"},{"time":753578,"text":"the challenges that women will face"},{"time":756285,"text":"in telling their stories is real,"},{"time":759077,"text":"but we need to start pursuing"},{"time":761782,"text":"and trying to identify mediums"},{"time":764269,"text":"to participate in our system"},{"time":765760,"text":"and not just pursue the media blindly."},{"time":770124,"text":"Today, more women than ever"},{"time":773122,"text":"are standing up and questioning"},{"time":774767,"text":"the government in India,"},{"time":776146,"text":"and this is a result of that courage."},{"time":779169,"text":"There is a sixfold increase in women"},{"time":782222,"text":"reporting harassment,"},{"time":783784,"text":"and the government passed"},{"time":785173,"text":"the Criminal Law (Amendment) Act in 2013"},{"time":788149,"text":"to protect women against sexual assault."}]},{"cues":[{"time":791968,"text":"As I end this talk,"},{"time":793920,"text":"I just want to say"},{"time":796040,"text":"that I know a lot of us in this room have our secrets,"},{"time":801620,"text":"but let us speak up."},{"time":803572,"text":"Let us fight the shame and talk about it."},{"time":806241,"text":"It could be a platform, a community,"},{"time":809761,"text":"your loved one, whoever or whatever you choose,"},{"time":813648,"text":"but let us speak up."},{"time":815740,"text":"The truth is, the end to this problem"},{"time":818800,"text":"begins with us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":820542,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822187,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}